## Description {#details}

This file defines the implementation of a filter that replaces symbolizer markup with human-readable expressions.

See <a href="https://llvm.org/docs/SymbolizerMarkupFormat.html">https://llvm.org/docs/SymbolizerMarkupFormat.html</a>
